definition:
A man of the tribe of Benjamin living at the time of Egypt and Wilderness, only mentioned at 1Ch.7.7; 
 son of: Bela (H1106A); 
 brother of: Ard (H0714H), Naaman (H5283H), Uzzi (H5813I), Uzziel (H5816I), Jerimoth (H3406), Iri (H5901), Addar (H0146H), Gera (H1617I), Abihud (H0031), Abishua (H0050H) and Ahoah (H0265)
 § Ezbon = "hasting to discern: I will be enlargement"
1) a son of Gad
2) grandson of Benjamin
